@startuml Due Diligence Export â€” User Level
title Due Diligence Package

actor "User" as user
participant "Due Diligence Page" as dd
participant "Preview" as preview
participant "Download" as dl

== Viewing Due Diligence Overview ==

user -> dd : Navigates to /due-diligence
user -> dd : Sees list of products with\ndue diligence readiness status

== Previewing Package Contents ==

user -> dd : Selects a product
dd -> preview : Shows preview of all sections:\n- Product information\n- SBOM summary\n- Vulnerability findings\n- License compliance\n- Technical file status\n- CRA report history\n- Stakeholder list\n- Compliance timeline
note right of preview : This is a read-only preview\nof everything that will be\nincluded in the export.

== Downloading ZIP Package ==

user -> preview : Clicks "Export ZIP"
preview -> dl : ZIP file downloads containing:\n- Product summary (JSON)\n- SBOM (CycloneDX + SPDX)\n- Vulnerability report\n- License compliance report\n- Technical documentation\n- Compliance timeline
note right of dl : Single ZIP file suitable\nfor sending to auditors,\nmarket surveillance, or\nsupply chain partners.

@enduml
